AUDIENCE: Metamorphosis.

00:30:57.980 --> 00:30:59.840
BOBBY MCFERRIN: Metamorphosis,
yeah.

00:30:59.840 --> 00:31:03.160
It's gone through all
kinds of things.

00:31:03.160 --> 00:31:06.010
