spirituals, in 1957, on the

00:31:15.200 --> 00:31:19.140
Riverside label called "Deep
River." And so I used that as

00:31:19.140 --> 00:31:22.290
a basis for this album.

00:31:22.290 --> 00:31:25.820
I didn't want to do it like my
dad because his was very--

00:31:25.820 --> 00:31:31.140
well, not classical but he had
a classical trained voice.

00:31:31.140 --> 00:31:33.810
I wanted to do something that
was a little more folksy and

00:31:33.810 --> 00:31:37.596
