You were the stars--

00:39:45.320 --> 00:39:45.680
MALE SPEAKER: Yeah,
what's up man.

00:39:45.680 --> 00:39:45.866
BOBBY MCFERRIN: [SINGING]

00:39:45.866 --> 00:39:47.150
--in your eyes.

