500 trillion times.

00:41:10.245 --> 00:41:12.485
[LAUGHTER]

00:41:12.485 --> 00:41:14.620
AUDIENCE: So how do you keep
making it new and magical?

00:41:14.620 --> 00:41:17.180
BOBBY MCFERRIN: I don't sing
it anymore in concert.

00:41:17.180 --> 00:41:21.250
I haven't sung it all the way
through in at least 20 years.

00:41:21.250 --> 00:41:25.100
It was probably like 1988,
1989, something like that

00:41:25.100 --> 00:41:29.550
because I got, basically, tired
of singing the song.

00:41:29.550 --> 00:41:34.500
Now the blessing is, nowadays,
I go on YouTube and I'll find

00:41:34.500 --> 00:41:36.760
these eight-year-old kids
singing [SINGING]

00:41:36.760 --> 00:41:40.360
