tune and singing it.

00:41:50.860 --> 00:41:53.660
They're playing it
in karaoke bars.

00:41:53.660 --> 00:41:55.560
Grunge bands are playing it.

00:41:55.560 --> 00:41:57.060
[LAUGHTER]

00:41:57.060 --> 00:41:59.150
BOBBY MCFERRIN: A cappella
groups are singing it.

00:41:59.150 --> 00:42:02.680
And it's just a blessing
for me.

