BOBBY MCFERRIN: Well,
just try it.

00:43:12.780 --> 00:43:13.700
MALE SPEAKER: [DEEP VOICE]

00:43:13.700 --> 00:43:14.533
In a-- no.

00:43:14.533 --> 00:43:15.016
BOBBY MCFERRIN: No.

