00:50:32.420 --> 00:50:33.720
You must have learned
how to make the

00:50:33.720 --> 00:50:35.215
car sound, for instance.

00:50:35.215 --> 00:50:37.860
That's, certainly, imitating
something.

00:50:37.860 --> 00:50:42.326
BOBBY MCFERRIN: Well, I use
what I hear, basically.

00:50:42.326 --> 00:50:43.200
AUDIENCE: Thanks.

00:50:43.200 --> 00:50:43.880
BOBBY MCFERRIN: [SINGING]

00:50:43.880 --> 00:50:44.950
You're welcome.

00:50:44.950 --> 00:50:46.540
Thank you.

00:50:46.540 --> 00:50:49.590
